snippet.title: The History of Johnny Depp And Amber Heard (Timeline, Audio And The Dangers Of Dating A Narcissist)
snippet.description:
In this video I talk about the history of Johnny Depp And Amber Heard. I also present you a timeline of the whole situation between the ex couple, play the recordings of some of the conversations they had during their marriage and divorce process, give my perspective on the whole situation, share mi thoughts on Johnny Depp and Amber Heard and I also Chat a little bit on what happens when you date a narcissist. (That last part is based on experience). 

What do you think of this whole situation? 
Who do you think is telling the Truth? 
Let me know in the comments below. 

Thank you for your time! 😊
